\id JAS James NT Yawu - Foreman 15/7/95
\h JEMS
\toc1 Jems eter bas rasem siglou
\toc2 Jems
\toc3 Jems
\mt1 JEMS
\mt2 Jems eter bas rasem siglou
\is1 Kiyi late tuma.
\ip Gwote siglou Jems ere bas rasen Juda Kristen tatame emne newopitim. Juda Kristen tatame eme emri kantri mesginen eme akeite akeite kantrike yin temenem. Eke Jems ere emne bebe porereken tuma emne etep kir bas rasem. Kem nowselri wos mane abote. Kem tame yaper, Satan, erne pekeroukte. Kem wule yenbowou tobobetete. Kem Jisas erne kenake abote. Kem tuma yenbowou wote. Kem ei mane naite. Kem kemri sig eisau maime mane wote. Kem Apei God eterken tuma namdete. Ete tumake Jems ere bas rasem.
\is1 Jems ere Kristen tatame etemne bas rasem tuma gwo.
\ip Sapta 1:1—18. Nemne seilabe woske nema muresen teten God eterke noub temente.
\io1 Sapta 1:19—5:6. Nema God erne kenawaike noub abote nenbe, nema wule yenbo sete.
\io1 Sapta 5:7-20. Nema muresen God eterken tuma namden Aneyen erne koute.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 An Jems, an God eterken Aneyen Jisas Kraisken etepri yaku kerebe tame. Kem Israelri ep yekwo let ep yekwo let tewo bor pes keyem (12-pela) tame beig. Kem Israel provins mesginin akeite akeite kantrike yikwute yakwutem. An kemne pir won kemne gwo siglou bas rasbe.
\s1 Nemne seilabe woske nema mure petbe.
\p 
\v 2 Ari geisimase, epkap epkap wos yaper kemne seilate, kem pap yaper mane tete. Kem etepke abote. E nerem metekwasbe wos.
\v 3 Wos yaper kemne seilate wote, kem God erne kenawaike abote. Kenawaike abote, kemne seilabe wos kem kuyese teitkwunen taskwurte.
\v 4 Kem som muresen taskwurte. Som taskwuren yin kem tatame yenbo ten kem Kristen sespe tete nenbe. Etepkap kem mure beke kip eikse.
\s1 Tatame eme porere yenbo eiksete, eme God erne wolate.
\p 
\v 5 Tatame eme porere eiksete, eme God erne wolate. Wolate, ere emne newote nenbe. Erne wolabe tatame God ere emne akei newote nenbe. Ere metekwasen kenake newobe. Ere eger beke kip te.
\v 6 Kem God erne wolate, kem kenawaike abon ek wolate. Kem porere pes mane tete. Porere pes tebe tatame eme ok sarekap. Marye yan ok sare tenbule tanbulebekap, eme etepkap.
\v 7-8 Porere pes tetan tatame eme wos nogwape abolawoibe. Abolawoibe, eme mane etep abote. Aneyen ere nemne newote.
\s1 Eikse akse tatameken sagmame tatameken etemne wobe tuma.
\p 
\v 9 Wos eikse Kristen tatame God ere emne sig yenbo newom, eke eme metekwaste.
\v 10 Sagmame Kristen tatame God ere emri sig teitkwunem, eke eme metekwaste. Beke an etep wobe? Me walku senin yan kerake ten ek sok tetebekap, sagmame tatame eme etepke tebe.
\v 11 Me walku yan buyen yabel pasen walku sok ten segitbe. Walku yenbo e yaper tebe. Sagmame tatame eme etepkap tebe. Eme tokwo pet yaku kerebe, eme yaper tete nenbe.
\s1 God ere nemne kobo labe.
\p 
\v 12 Som taskwurbe tatame eme metekwaste. Emne seilabe wos eme kuyese taskwuren God erne pap som yewobe. Etep tebe, God ere kiyi womkap, eme etep som noub temente nenbe.
\v 13 Tatame eme wule yaper nente abobe, eme mane etep wote. God eter ane seilabe, eke an wos yaper nenye. Berai. Eme etep mane wote. God ere nemne beke seila. God ere tame emne wule yaper nente beke seila.
\v 14 Tatame emne seilabe wule e gwopkap. Tatame wurare wurare eme emri porerek wule yaper nente abobe. Emri porere yaper emne wobe, eke eme wule yaper nente abobe.
\v 15 Emri porerek eme wule yaper nente abobe, sene eme wos yaper ek nenbe. Eke, eme wule yaper kenake nogwon nogwon yin eme me sate nenbe.
\p 
\v 16 Ari geisimase yenbo, kem yikwokwo tuma mane etep abote. God ere nemne wule yaper nente seilabe. Ete tuma eme me yikwokwobe.
\v 17 Yenbotanbo wos nogwape e Hevenke yabe. Lup yabel sow seikim tame, Apei God eter, ere yenbo woswou newobe tame. Ere wule yenbowou nenbe, ere wule kenakena beke nen.
\v 18 Eteri selpapke ere noub abon tuma seken womke, nema eteri tatame tem. Etepkap, nema mase tobo yenkap, nema taresi tatamekap. Akeite tatameken akeite wosken eme kin yekwok tetan.
\s1 Nema tuma noub meten tobote.
\p 
\v 19 Ari geisimase yenbo, kem sene abo. Kem tuma agetage noub met. Kem tuma agetage awosein mane wote. Kem pap agetage mane wayete.
\v 20 Pap wayebe tatame eme God eteri wule yenbo beke nen.
\v 21 Eke kem wurare wurare wule yapersaper mesginte. Kem God eteri kulke wurin eter kemri selpapke wobe tuma eteke noub meten nente. Ete mureken tumak kem yenbo tete.
\p 
\v 22 God eteri tuma kem metem, kem noub beke met. Kem maime tuma me yikwokwobe. Kem eteri tuma noub meten kir tobote, e yenbo.
\v 23 Tame ere God eri tuma meten beke kip nen, ere eteri bitimi maime oknalke labe tamekap.
\v 24 Ere bitimi lan mesginbe, eri laye bitimi ere maime agetage sene eiksebe.
\v 25 Kem etepkap mane tete. Tatame eme God eteri tuma bas rasten siglou noub late, eme metekwaste nenbe. Etep tebe tatame eme tuma meten beke eikse. Eme noub meten tobobetete, wule yaper ere ete tame emne beke kip keresuk. Berai. God eteri tuma eme peten porere yenboken noub sewurbe.
\p 
\v 26 Kau tatame eme etep wobe. Nema God eteri wule sebe. Etep wobe tatame, kem noub met. Sene kem yikwokwo tuma o pap waye tuma wobe, etepkap kem maime tuma me yikwokwon wobe. Etepkap wobe, kerem tobobe wule ere oksubu yite nenbe.
\v 27 God eteri wule tobobe tatame eme gwopkapke nenbe, Apei God ere labe, eme wule yenbowai, more wule seken nenbe. Eme gwopke nenbe. Eme kuwon yenken wane taken emne yin kobo labe. Wos wuri eme kir nenbe. Eme nowselri wule amekwunen selpap yenbowou nenbe. Etepkap tebe, eme yaper beke kip te.
\c 2
\s1 Nema tatame nogwape emne wule wurisubuke nenbetete.
\p 
\v 1 Ari geisimase, neremri Aneyen Jisas Krais ere Heven maime. Kem erne kenawaike abobe. Etepkap kem tatame emne wule kenakena mane nente.
\v 2 An wobe, kap tame pes epe God erne sukye woran keremken site wote, kap wuri ere sagken tame ere kerap yenbo wolen ring yenbo let borke wun akek wurte. Kap wuri ere eikse akse tame, ere kerap yaper wolen akek wurin etek kir site nenbe.
\v 3 Kap kem epne wule pes nente o? Kerap yenbo woleten tame kem erne noub abon etep wote. Sen, ne gwo wolbaye yenbok yan site. Etep wote, sene kem eikse akse tame erne pir beke kip wo, erne wolbaye beke kip newo. Kem erne etep wote. Ne etek tetete, o ne neremri tewo tobok yan selke site. Kem etep mane nente.
\v 4 Etepkap nenbe tame eme selpap yaper, eme tatame emne sin lan emne wule kenakena nenbe.
\p 
\v 5 Ari geisimase yenbo, kem noub met. God ere eikse akse tatame emne wom, eme erne kenawaike abobe, eme God eteri komke yite. God ere etep wom. Ane pap yewobe tatame eme areri komke yite. Etep wom.
\v 6 Kerem kem eikse akse tatame emne wule yaper nenbe. An kemne wometbe. Eike kemne wule yaper nenbe? Eike kemne tuma namdebe? Eikse akse tame eme kemne etep beke nen. Berai. Sagken tame etem eme kemne etep tebe.
\v 7 Kem Krais Jisas eteri sig yenbo petem. Eike ete sig workwoyeken resbe? Sagken tatame etem etep tebe.
\p 
\v 8 God eteri siglou etep wobe. Kem maime pap yewon noub eyarbekap, kem tatame emne noub etep eyarbetete. Kem ete wule tobote, kem wule yenbo nente.
\v 9 Kem tatame emne wule kenakena nente, kem yaperke nenbe. Etep tebe, kem God eteri wule tousibe. Ere kemne tuma namdete.
\v 10 Tatame eme wule nogwape tobote, eme wule wurisubu tousite, ete tatame eme wule akei tousibe. Eme wule tousibe tatame.
\v 11 God eter ere wule newobe tame. Ere etep wobe. Kem sir bisi mane yite. Ere etep kir wobe. Kem alwo mane pete. Ere etep wobe. Tame ere sir bisi beke yi, ere alwo pete nenbe, ete tame ere wule tousibe.
\v 12 God eteri wulek ere kemne peikmenem wule yaper ogorasem. Ete wulek ere keremri wobekap keremri nenbekap neburolate nenbe, eke kem ete wule eteri kulke wurin tuma yenbo wobetete, wule yenbo nenbetete.
\v 13 Kem ek met. Kobo beke la tatame God ere emne tuma namden emne kobo beke kip la. Kobo labe tatame God ere emne kobo awosein late nenbe. Kobo labe wule ere tuma namdebe wule teitkwunbe.
\s1 Tame ere God erne kenawaike abobe, wule yenbo beke abon nen, eteri abobekap ete oksubu yite nenbe.
\p 
\v 14 Ari geisimase, tame ere etep wobe. An Krais erne kenawaike abobe. Ere etep wobe, sene ere wule yenbo beke kip nen, eter abobekap ete oksubu yite nenbe. Etep tebe, God ere erne mapeke sene pette?
\v 15 Kap Kristen geisi o mase eme kerap wole wos yaper warbe, eme a berai,
\v 16 kem emne mane etepkap wote. Ne tame oub warte. Ne yin a an noub temen. God ere kemne kobo late. Kem etep bepou me wobe, kem erne wos beke newo, e kem tumasubuke wobe, kem emne yenbo beke nen. Berai.
\v 17 Eke kenawaike abobe wulewou kuyese beke kip te. Ere wule yenbo kir beke kip nen, ere oksubu yite, ere sa tamekap tete.
\p 
\v 18 Kap tame ere etep wote. Tame wuri ere God erne kenawaike abobe, tame wuri ere wule yenbo nenbe. Metye. Kenawaike abobe wule nema mapeke late? An wule yenbo nenbe, an ari God erne kenawaike abobe wule nene kuyese peterabe.
\v 19 Ne kenawaike etep abobe. God wurisubuke tetan. Ne etep kenawaike abobe, etepkap e kuyese berai. Omugabo peikri sikilewas etem kir eme God eterne metten. Eme metten, eke eme aken negnegbe.
\v 20 Ne worisubu tetan tame. Kap an nene peterate? Ne God erne abon yenbo wos beke nen, nereri kenawaike abobekap e oksubu yibe.
\v 21 Neremri warege Abraham ere God eteri tuma kenawaike meten eteri yen, Aisak, erne kwar pete tiyke rasem. God ere eter nenem yenbo wos lam, ere erne tame yenbo wom.
\v 22 Kem metten. Abraham ere God erne kenawaike abobetem, God eter womkap ere etep kir nenbetem. Etep tebetem, eter nenbetem wuleken eter kenawaike abobetem wuleken epe kirkir tem.
\v 23 God eteri siglou etep wobe. Abraham ere God erne kenawaike abom, eke God ere erne tame yenbo wom. God ere Abraham erne tamenowu yenbo wom.
\v 24 Kem metten. Tame ere God erne bepou me kenawaike abobe, ere wule yenbo kir beke nen, God ere erne etep beke kip wo. Ne tame yenbo. Berai. Tame ere God erne kenawaike abon wule yenbo kir nenbe, God ere erne etep wobe. Ne tame yenbo. Etep wobe.
\p 
\v 25 Kiyi temenem sir bisi yibetem ta, Rahap, te etepwou tem, te wule yenbo nenem. Juda tame pes epe ei kase late yim, te epne peten noub berasen akeite keluke won yim, peiktame eme epne beke pe. Etep tem, God ere tene ta yenbo wom.
\v 26 Wusom ere wouken berai, ete wusom ere sabe tamekap. Eke, tatame eme God erne kenawaike abobe, eme wule yenbo beke nen, ete tatame emri kenawaike abobe wule e sabe tamekap.
\c 3
\s1 Nema neremri tawul noub lakerete.
\p 
\v 1 Ari geisimase, kem nogwape kem God eteri tuma wusoube tame tete mane abote. Tatame mapsein e yau. God ere Kristen tatame nogwape emne sin lan tuma elen me namdete. Ere nemne tuma wusoube tame nemne sin lan kuken wote nenbe.
\v 2 Nema akei, nema be wos be wos yaper abon nenbe. Eike tatame eme tuma yenbowou wobe, eme tatame yenbo. Eme maime wusom kuyese lakeren wos yaper beke kip nen.
\v 3 Tame eme ain nebule peten hos eri elemoike rasen peikbe. Peikbe, ere hos erne kuyese kerepit peteyabe. Etep tebe, tame emri wobekap hos ere etek yibe.
\v 4 Sene kem sip kir abote. Sip eme eisau. Sip kerepit peteyabe wos, ete wos nebule. Marye yabe yabel ok sare ere ete sip erne peten gare okke yibetbe. Sene sip maime ere akeite emik yite nenbe, ere ete kerepit peteyabe wos emne sene kerepit peteyate, sip ere etek kuyese ek yibe.
\v 5 Tatame etemri tawul e wos nebule. Ete tawul nebulek wobe tuma, eme maime me gabebe.
\p Kem ker nebule kir abote. Tame eme gub taimebekap sene ker ere nebulek eyin yin ere eisau ten ere gub akei kuyese eyin yin sumabe.
\v 6 Tawul ere kerkap. Ere wos yapersaper wusom maime lisbe. Ete ker ere ker tetan komke yam ker. Ere nemne yaper nenbe. Ere tatame nogwape emne yaper nenbe.
\v 7 Akeite akeite boulri wos, portoub, om ap, mugwor wase, tame eme emne peten lei newon noub lakerebe. Kiyi temenem tame etem kir eme etep tebetem.
\v 8 Etep tebe, tame eme etemri tawul maime mapeke tagwom kerete. Eke, tawul ere tuma yapersaper wobe. Erne mapeke wotake? Ere tame tabe sopokap.
\v 9 Ete tawulke nema Keryen God erne pir wobe. Sene ete tawulwouke nema God erne eterkap seikim tame emne sou yogwu etek sene worabe.
\v 10 Elemoi wurisubuk nema tuma yenboken tuma yaperken wobe. Ari geisimase, nema etepkap mane tete.
\v 11 Ok sekbe emi e ok yenboken ok yaperken wurik etep beke sek. Berai.
\v 12 Ari geisimase, wate nawobe mane supa etek beke kip ya. Keibe nawobe etepwou wate beke kip etek tuk. Etepkap, gare ok ere ok yenbo beke kip te.
\s1 Tatame eme porere yenbo tetan, eme wule yenbo nente.
\p 
\v 13 Eike porere selpap yenbo tetan? Wule yenbo elen me nenbe tatame eme maime sig eisau beke wo. Nema etem yenbo nenbekap labe, nema metbe, eme porereken tatame.
\v 14 Kem tatame emne yaper abon pap wayebe, o kem maimewou abobe, ete wule yaper kem maime mane gabete. Be wos yaper kem abobe, kem mane berasen tuma yikwokwote.
\v 15 Etepkap porere yaper God ere kemne beke newo. Berai. E nowselri porere. Ete porere e por wale etemri porerekap. E Satan eter newobe porere ete.
\v 16 Tatame eme tatame emne yaper abon pap wayebe, o maimewou kena abobe, eme noub beke kip te. Eme ei naibe, eme nogwape epkap epkap wule yaper kir nenbe.
\v 17 Tatame eme God eter newobe porere selpap petbe, eme gwopke tebe. Kiyi nema etep wobe. Eme porere selpap yenbowai tetan. Sene nema etep wobe. Eme ei beke kip nai. Eme tuma elen me wobe. Eme wan beke gwole. Eme tatame emne kobo labe, eme emne yenbowou nenbe. Eme emne wule wurisubuke peterabe. Eme tuma beke yikwokwo.
\v 18 Ei gerube tame eme now sag nanekwobe tamekap. Tame eme now sag nanekwon yuri supa yenbo yabekap ete tame eme ei gerube, eme nenbe wule e yenbo.
\c 4
\s1 Nowselri wule tobobe tatame eme God eteri peiktame.
\p 
\v 1 Beke kem walekap naibe? Beke kem awoawo ei naibe? Kem selpap yaper tetan, kem be wos be wos yaper abon pap wayebe, eke kem ei naibe.
\v 2 Kem wos nogwape pette abobe, kem wos beke pet. Beke pet, eke kem tame pen sabe. Kem wos malbe, kem wos beke pet. Wos beke pet, kem ei kenake naibe. Kem God erne beke womet, eke kem wos beke pet.
\v 3 Kem selpap yaperke maime abon wometbe, eke kemri wometbe wos kem beke kip pet.
\v 4 Kem sir yibe tatamekap. Kem beke abo, tatame eme nowselri wule tobobe, ere God eteri peiktame tebe. Nowselri wule yaper nowu wurbe tatame eme God eteri peiktame seken.
\v 5 God eteri siglou etepke wobe. God ere etepke abobe. Ere nemne newom wou ere God eteri kulke temente, e yenbo. Etep wobe, kem mapeke abobe? God ere ete tuma bepou me wobe o berai?
\p 
\v 6 Etep tebe, tewok tewok God ere nemne kobo lan noub nenbe, nema maime teitkwunbe. God eteri siglou etep wobe.
\q1 Maime beke abo tatame God ere emne kobo lan noub nenbe.
\q1 Maime kenake gabebe tatame God ere emne teitkwunbe.
\m Etep wom.
\v 7 Eke, kem God eteri kulke wurin tete. Kem Satan erne naswoyin wotaketek, ere kemne mesginen amete.
\v 8 Kem God erne mekinwaike yite, ere etepwou, ere kemne mekinke temente. Kem wule yaper nenbe tatame kem porere yenbo pet. Kem porere pes tetan tatame kem porere yaper mesginte.
\v 9 Kem me kerate. Kem sou sak sene mane keyete, kem mokwowouke site. Kem mane metekwaste. Kem pap yaper met.
\v 10 Kem Keryen God eteri tewo tobok yan gulke pate. Etep tete, ere kemne nenewayen tetruwun kemne tuma yenbo wote.
\s1 Kem geisimase emne tuma mane namdete.
\p 
\v 11 Geisimase, kem Kristen geisimase emne tuma yaper mane wote. Geisimase emne tuma yaper wote tatame, o geisimase emne tuma namdete tatame eme yaperke nenbe. Etep tebe, eme God eteri wule yaper won namdebe. Etepkap tatame eme God eteri wule yenbo beke tobo. Berai. Eme ete wule yenbo erne sin lan namdebe.
\v 12 Wule newobe tame, tatame emne tuma namdebe tame wurisubuke tetan. E God eter. Eterwou ere tatame emne sene pette, o emne pen sate. Kerem, kem etepkap kuyese beke kip nen. Etepkap, kem tatame emne mane tuma namdete.
\s1 Nema wan mane gwolete.
\p 
\v 13 Kau kem etep wobe. Kipi o kwokwos nema taunke yin nabe wuri nema yaku etek keren kel nogwape pette. Etep wobe tame kem ari tuma noub mette.
\v 14 Kipi tete woskap kem beke met. Kem tatame, kem ei gwankap. Gwan e som beke te. Keni ei gwan kitbe. Kerake ten sene ei gwan berabe. Kem etepkap.
\v 15 Kem gwopke wote. Aneyen ere kir wote, nema som tete, nema etek yin ten yaku kerebetete. Etepke wote, e yenbo.
\v 16 Kem etepkap beke wo. Berai. Kemri nenbekap kem etep maime gabebe, e yaper.
\v 17 Wule yenbo metten tame ere ete wule yenbo beke kip nen, ere yaperke nenbe.
\c 5
\s1 Sagmame tatame eme yaper tete.
\p 
\v 1 Sagmame tatame nogwape kem noub met. Wos yaper kemne tete nenbe. Eke kem kera tayeken wayete nenbe.
\v 2 Keremri wos nogwape akei e kupa tem. Kemri tame oub sesegwan keren eme akei regyewom.
\v 3 Yuri tete yabel mekin mekinten, kem be wos be wos nogwape tuken akek rasten. Eke kemri rasten golken silvaken yuri eme yaper tete nenbe. Etep tete, e nemne me peterabe, kemri wusom kerke ei nenbekap. Ete peterabe.
\v 4 Metye. Kemri now yaku kerebe tame emne kem yikwokwon tokwo tep petem. Ete tokwo tep eme wobe, God ere kemne yaper awosein nente. Mure eisauken Keryen God ere ete now yaku kerebe tame emri kera taye metem.
\v 5 Kem nowselke temenem, kem be wos be wos yenbotanbo nogwape temenem, kem kenake metekwasbetem. Kem awos nogwape an wus ginirik sirbekap kemne pen sate yabel tete nenbe.
\v 6 Kem wos yaper beke nen tatame emne tuma namden pen sabetem. Ete tame eme kemne beke wotake, eme kemken awosein beke nai.
\s1 Nema mure peten taskwuren Aneyen erne koute.
\p 
\v 7 Geisimase, kem taskwuren Aneyen ere sene yate yabel som koute. Kem labe, now yaku kerebe tame eme noub som koube tame. Kiyi eme sag nanekwobetem. Sene eme mouken yabelken koube. Yuri ete wos eme okwobe, eme kwuten o peren ek abe.
\v 8 Etepkap, kem mure peten noub koute. Aneyen ere sene yate mekin mekinye, eke kem taskwuren noub koute.
\p 
\v 9 Geisimase, kem ei awosein mane nakosete. God ere ei nakosebe tatame emne tuma namdete nenbe. Metye. Tuma namdete nenbe tame ere eruke tetten.
\v 10 Geisimase, kem God eteri kiyiri tuma wusoubetem tame etem tebetemkap abote. Eme Aneyen eteri sigke tuma wusoubetem, eme mus eisau meten taskwurbetem. Kem etepke tobobetete.
\v 11 Nema etep wobe. Tatame eme me taskwurbe, eme metekwasbe tatame. Etep wobe. Job eteri tebetemkap kem etep metten. Ere mus eisau meten taskwurbetem. Sene Keryen God ere erne eyarem. Keryen ere papmame tame, ere tatame emne kobo lan noub eyarbe.
\s1 Nema tame kupa mane takte.
\p 
\v 12 Ari geisimase, an kemne tuma eisau wuri wote. Kem tame kupa mane takte. Kem kir tete, kem kir tete. Kem tuma abote, kem tuma abote. Kem nelri wos o nowselri wos o akeite wosri sig mane wote. Kem tame kupa takte, God ere kemne tuma namdete.
\s1 Tatame yenbo etem God erken namdebe tuma God ere noub metbe.
\p 
\v 13 Be wos yaper e keremne temente wote, kem Apei erken namdete. Kem pap oksubu tete wote, kem God erne sekwo lomen erne sig eisau wobetete.
\v 14 Kap ta o tame eme kapoyi meten wote, eme Kristen apeilake emne won yate. Yate, eme etemken siyewon Aneyen eteri sigke kapoyi met tatame emne kwar wuske keren God erne womette, ere ete tatame emne kobo late.
\v 15 Eme God erne worwor womette, ete kapoyi yenbo tete. God ere erne mure newote, ete tatame eme sene yenbo tete nenbe. Eme kap kiyi wule yaper wuri nenem, God ere ete wule yaper peten sepitte, erne tuma beke kip namde.
\v 16 Etepkap, kerem nenbe wule yaper kem Kristen geisimase etemken awoawo wusowun emken awoawo abon Apei erne womette. Etep tete, kapoyi yenbo tete. Tatame yenbo etem God erken namdebe tuma God ere noub meten nenbe.
\v 17 Elaija ere neremkap tame, ere God erne worwor etep wometbetem. Mou mane tite. Etep wometbetem, God ere mou beke won ti, nabe tep wuri wiwi mur mou beke ti.
\v 18 Sene ere God erne mou tite wometemke, mou sene ek tim. Timke, awos sene noub rekwan yam.
\s1 Tame ere God erne mesginte, nema erne sene wopette.
\p 
\v 19 Ari geisimase, keremri wuri ere God eteri wule seken mesginen kelu yaperke yite, sene akeite Kristen tatame eme erne kobo lan ere God eteri wule sene tobote, e yenbo.
\v 20 Kem noub abote. Eike tame eme etepkap wule yaper nenbe tame erne kelu yenbok panen yite, etem eme eri wou sene petbekap, ere beke kip sa, ere yenbo som temente. God ere ete tame eri nenbetem wule yaper nogwape akei peten sepitte, ere erne tuma sene beke kip namde.
\p Jems eter bas rasem tuma ab eteke. 
